common_options.name: -c
common_options.tip: read hashsums from the FILEs and check them

common_options.name: -q
common_options.tip: don't print OK for each successfully verified file

common_options.name: -s
common_options.tip: don't output anything, status code shows success

common_options.name: --strict
common_options.tip: exit non-zero for improperly formatted checksum lines

common_options.name: -w
common_options.tip: warn about improperly formatted checksum lines

common_options.name: -z
common_options.tip: end each output line with NUL, not newline

common_options.name: --no-names
common_options.tip: Omits filenames in the output (option not present in GNU/Coreutils)
